HEADWORD: Dennet
<hw>Den"net</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A light, open,
two-wheeled carriage for one horse; a kind of gig.</def> (⟦ldquo⟧The
term and vehicle common about 1825.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Latham.</au>)⟦br⟧
